Package processors

Class ShellProcessor

  • java.lang.Object
    • processors.Processor
      • processors.ShellProcessor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IProcessor
    public class ShellProcessor
extends Processor
    A sub-class of Processor which makes use of the CommandRunner class to run the commands found in code chunks. Code chunks are executed, and the resulting output is "spliced" together with the non-code (document) chunks to produce an output document.
